author: By MIKE HOUSEHOLDER and ED WHITE Associated Press
title: Thousands protest Michigan governor's social distance order
description: The ‘Operation Gridlock’ protest was organized by the Michigan Conservative Coalition.
content:
LANSING, Mich. (AP) Thousands of flag-waving, honking protesters drove past the Michigan Capitol on Wednesday to show their displeasure with Gov. Gretchen Whitmers orders to keep people at home and businesses locked during the coronavirus outbreak.
